casebody.data:
Barbara J. WILLIAMS, Respondent,
v.
Reginald E. WILLIAMS, Appellant. No. ED 106951 Missouri Court of Appeals, Eastern District, DIVISION ONE. Filed: May 21, 2019 FOR APPELLANT: Aleksandra Hudson, 120 South Central Avenue, Suite 150, Clayton, MO 63105. FOR RESPONDENT: Barbara J. Williams, Acting Pro Se, Before Roy L. Richter, P.J., Mary K. Hoff, J., and Robert M. Clayton III, J.

ORDER

PER CURIAM.

Reginald E. Williams appeals the trial court's judgment granting in part and denying in part his Motion to Modify Child Support and Calculate Amounts Due and Owing he filed against Barbara J. Williams. We find no error has occurred.

No jurisprudential purpose would be served by a written opinion. We have, however, provided the parties a memorandum setting forth the reasons for our decision. The trial court's judgment is affirmed under Rule 84.16(b).
